Use Case	                      Shared By	                        Description
Search Artworks	                Visitor, Curator	                Visitors search for inspiration; curators search for pieces to exhibit.
Explore Museums	                Visitor, Curator	                Visitors browse museums to visit; curators explore venues for exhibitions.
Check Museum Hours	            Visitor, Curator	                Visitors plan visits; curators schedule events and logistics.
Select Canvas Sizes	            Curator, Administrator	          Curators choose sizes for artworks; administrators manage the catalog.
Manage Artist Records	          Curator, Administrator	          Curators may update artist info for exhibitions; administrators maintain the database.
Import/Export Data	            Curator, Administrator	          Curators may bulk upload exhibition data; administrators handle system-wide imports.

Actor	                          Use Case	                        Description
Visitor	                        View Artist Profiles	            Browse artist details like name, style, nationality, birth/death.
Visitor	                        Search Artworks	                  Find artworks by artist, style, or canvas size.
Visitor	                        Explore Museums	                  View museum details including location, contact, and website.
Visitor	                        Check Museum Hours	              See opening and closing times for each day.
Curator	                        Assign Artworks to Museums	      Link artworks to specific museums for exhibitions.
Curator	                        Schedule Exhibitions	            Plan and manage exhibition dates and times.
Curator	                        Select Canvas Sizes	              Choose appropriate canvas dimensions for artworks.
Administrator	                  Manage Artist Records	            Add, update, or delete artist information.
Administrator	                  Manage Museum Data	              Maintain museum addresses, contacts, and URLs.
Administrator	                  Manage Canvas Size                Catalog	Update available canvas dimensions.
Administrator	                  Import/Export Data	              Upload or download CSV files for bulk data management.
